{{one source|date=May 2023}}
{{Infobox religious building|religious_affiliation=[[Shinto]]|image=Namba-yasaka-jinja haiden1.jpg|deity=[[Susanoo-no-Mikoto]]|type=[[Gion shrine]]}}

Nanba Shrine is a [[Shinto Shrine]] in [[Osaka]]. It is a shrine for [[Gion worship]] dedicated to [[Susanoo-no-Mikoto]].<ref>{{Cite web|last=Quin|first=Rebecca|date=2020-01-11|title=Namba Yasaka Shrine|url=https://travel.gaijinpot.com/namba-yasaka-shrine/|access-date=2023-05-13|website=GaijinPot Travel|language=en}}</ref>

It has a large lion-shaped building which is famous in Japan.<ref>{{Cite web|title=Namba Yasaka Shrine|url=https://insideosaka.com/namba-yasaka-shrine/|access-date=2023-05-13|website=Inside Osaka|language=en-US}}</ref>
[[File:Namba_Yasaka-jinja.jpg|thumb]]

